add black as formatter

I'll add Black as the formatter for Python in your Zed settings file.

<patch>
<title>Add Black as Python formatter</title>
<edit>
<path>app/.zed/settings.json</path>
<description>Set Black as the formatter for Python in Zed settings</description>
<operation>update</operation>
<old_text>            "formatter":
        }
    }
}</old_text>
<new_text>            "formatter": "black"
        }
    }
}</new_text>
</edit>
</patch>
